sql:
SELECT user_id, COUNT(DISTINCT business_id) AS business_count
FROM reviews
GROUP BY user_id;

external_knowledge:
- A business is considered to have at least one review if its review count is greater than 0; 
- The ranking of businesses is based on their review counts in descending order within each city; 
- Average star ratings may be 'No Reviews Yet' if no reviews exist.

sql:
